    Let test2_result be test_unterminated_string_handling
    Set total_tests to total_tests plus 1
    If test2_result:
        Set passed_tests to passed_tests plus 1
    Otherwise:
        Set failed_tests to failed_tests plus 1
    
    Note: Test indentation error handling
    Let test3_result be test_indentation_error_handling
